{"tid":2227063,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過突然少/無汗出?","createTime":"2020-10-02T13:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T13:07:10.000Z","uid":1842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f6ff2450c366e5348ecf4f672a0a5ca39d9ba876","tid":2227063,"uid":1842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T13:02:54.000Z","msg":"由細都大都好大汗<br />\n講緊夏天屋企換完衫等出街都已經出晒汗，做完運動個時就直情好似倒水咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢排出街同做運動都少左好多汗(唔關天氣事，以往就算涼涼地都好多汗出)<br />\n尤其做運動個時得個身有出汗，手腳都無乜汗出，個人又好似好焗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下有無人試過咁，係咪身體邊到出左事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4f8138585827ea76e08b44587c8cfd9b63896b","tid":2227063,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T13:05:39.000Z","msg":"你就嚟死喇"},{"pid":"25c16262fd58030f0940bbc07fae3b10434e2e89","tid":2227063,"uid":164497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f4f8138585827ea76e08b44587c8cfd9b63896b","tid":2227063,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T13:05:39.000Z","msg":"你就嚟死喇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T13:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}